Once PLM Has Been Named, this powerful computer instrument has been used to design assembly lines of manufacturing factories in all the world, plants of energy, instruments of high accuracy.
The goal is to reproduce, to simulate faithfully the product or the process before building it in a real way, preventing failures and avoidable expenses this way.
PLM has facilitated the development of the cameras of Canon, of the airplanes of Sukhoi or of the most famous utilitarian cars of Nissan.
